column1: NOTES: (1) The European  Internet Stats are estimates for June 30, 2019. (2) Facebook subscriber data are estimates for Dec 31, 2018. (3) Detailed data for individual countries may be  found by clicking on each country name. (4) The population numbers are for  mid-year 2019 based mainly on data the United Nations Population Division. (5) The usage numbers come from various sources, mainly from statistics  published by Nielsen Online , ITU , Facebook , GfK, and other trustworthy local sources. (6) For definitions and help, see the  site  surfing guide. (7) Data may be cited, giving due credit and establishing an active link back to www.internetworldstats.com . © Copyright 2019, Miniwatts Marketing Group. All rights reserved  worldwide.
